&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a hard working, enthusiastic, and motivated individual to complement our existing, expanding nursing team within the Gynaecology/Colposcopy outpatients department. Gynaecology OPD is an ever expanding service with huge opportunities to learn . This is a Monday to Friday role but flexible hours will be considered with an opportunity to rotate between outpatients and inpatients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested/or have experience in the field of Gynaecology we are keen to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date - 18th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Laura Groves&lt;/p&gt;
